window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b>The complete version of <i>The Gathering Storm</i> will be available on October 27, 2009. This prologue is included in the complete version. However if you want to hear it early you can get it here now.</b><br><p> The prologue of the long-awaited conclusion to Robert Jordan's fantasy masterpiece. This selection features a bonus recording of Robert Jordan's widow and longtime editor, Harriet McDougal, discussing the process of continuing the Wheel of Time series after Jordan's death, and how they came to select Brandon Sanderson to carry the torch.</p>"; 
